{"tid":1535534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[跳閘] 新閘撞唔開","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:45:43.000Z","uid":57637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f17b0dbf2ff58b7940d73a681d80d9bcde08846","tid":1535534,"uid":57637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"用大脾撞唔得<br />\n係咪要大力d"},{"pid":"89a8d3c8c572ece187fd10b389016ad59df1b0db","tid":1535534,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"練肌肉"},{"pid":"64990e391010474c6d8d3ad264b4ffd60e337b16","tid":1535534,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:34:18.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"d6f1f9e75c2d04d849058efe8e35a265c7880f65","tid":1535534,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"Laam過去/跟住前面出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0b8420897273db26b396b99b2a6ed3b5987c77","tid":1535534,"uid":143699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=a834675b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"28daba918a9895d1f1dcc7ebdfe66ef536f586c8","tid":1535534,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"助跑 撞鬆左就大家都撞得過"},{"pid":"7bc00ff92ee29bd75c91a1d69ef666fca49a4817","tid":1535534,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:42:55.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n5. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n6. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n7. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n8. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n9. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"56151c20ba852c71a30d6cb70d00c6dca871a4bd","tid":1535534,"uid":57637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f1f9e75c2d04d849058efe8e35a265c7880f65","tid":1535534,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"Laam過去/跟住前面出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"怕醜<br />\n<br />\n而家撞唔開<br />\n直接跳<br />\n<br />\n有d 驚仆街"},{"pid":"dd742a3228d63eb02437dc8a796ebd5c0b1cb75d","tid":1535534,"uid":57637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"旺角個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81654a408ac8858850f949c0ca5f594c39d182a","tid":1535534,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"撞唔開"},{"pid":"cfd5da4e60232377a45d54eef184acc2bbe43d4d","tid":1535534,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"新閘正常係推唔開 要跳了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都驚"}]}